LineageOS 16.0:

1. Removed the built-in input method and browser, replacing them with Via and Gboard respectively;

2. Removed redundant VNDK libraries: vndk28, vndk-sp28, vndk26, and vndk-sp26 in the system/lib and system/lib64 directories;

3. Removed the @x.x-service binaries for vendor.huawei.hardware.biometrics.hwfacerecognize, vendor.huawei.hardware.tp, vendor.huawei.hardware.sensors, vendor.huawei.hardware.power, vendor.huawei.hardware.otherdevices, vendor.huawei.hardware.light, vendor.huawei.hardware.hwfactoryinterface, and vndk-sp26;

4. Removed the Huawei Supplier HAL (see point 3);

5. Removed the corresponding HAL startup scripts (see point 3). (Points).

lineageOS 17.1:

1. Removed the built-in input method and browser, replacing them with Via and Gboard respectively;

2. Removed redundant VNDK libraries: vndk26, vndk-sp26, vndk28, vndk-sp28, vndk29, and vndk-sp29 in the system/lib and system/lib64 directories;

